       <td>
	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">A personal account of one aspiring game designer's experience at Fanguard Beta</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Sigswat</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Aug  2, 2005, 11:16</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=A%20personal%20account%20of%20one%20aspiring%20game%20designer%27s%20experience%20at%20Fanguard%20Beta&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_1.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="http://www.thesafehouse.org/articles/events/printer_1.php">Printer&nbsp;friendly&nbsp;page</a></div>
	  <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="/cgi-bin/articles/exec/goforum.cgi?id=1&cat=26">Discuss this story</a></div>
	  </td>
      </tr>
